================================================================================
The inference engine is a dependency, not part of this fork
================================================================================

Relais is the application layer. The on-device inference engine, LiteRT-LM
(com.google.ai.edge.litertlm), ships as a prebuilt binary Maven artifact under
its own terms (Apache-2.0). Relais forks the app, not the engine, and depends on
LiteRT-LM as an external, separately-licensed component.


